Entries.default: "Should we maybe consider not touching anything? Just... for once?"
"I am not eager to visit Ngati's coral hall. Take care what you do."
"I have a feeling I'm not going to like what happens next."
"Never seen one of these machines that was anything but trouble."
"As impressive as these Engwithan machines are, they are always dangerous."
"Machine this old and salty? Figure it be twice like to break as not."
"That there is the legacy of the gods."
